{"tid":57525,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普下苦功！利物浦上下每個人他都叫得出名","createTime":"2016-12-28T05:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T09:33:49.000Z","uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d85442f34413f325cf52e295c0eea4367ca41bbc","tid":57525,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"利物浦教練高普稱，他用了一年時間，現在已經可以叫出紅軍訓練基地每個工作人員的名字了。他認為，這種個人之間的親密關係，有助於營造良好氛圍。<br />\n<br />\n　　「<span style=\"color: red;\">我們上週舉辦了聖誕派對，和去年有很大的不同，」高普說，「在經過一年以後，我已經認識了所有人。而在剛來三個月時，有幾個工作人員的名字我還叫不上來。」</span><br />\n<br />\n　　「在訓練基地，我們擁有這種非常好的氣氛，這全都要感謝在那裡工作的所有人。這和我在多蒙特時的情況雖有不同，但也很近似，這種氛圍很好。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我現在依然和很多多蒙特球員有聯繫，希望將來如果我離開利物浦了，也能和這些紅軍球員保持聯絡，因為他們都是很好的小夥子。但是，他們在這支球隊，不是因為他們都是好小夥子，而因為他們都是傑出的球員，我喜歡和他們一起工作，我很感謝他們。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高爸爸</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7598442726abbb411f74a9213f00986c3872644f","tid":57525,"uid":3132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3525386264c664a028b09f7b0feedc871195b6","tid":57525,"uid":1017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高daddy"},{"pid":"4876306c894b724099d9dc9e257421870107d3db","tid":57525,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"父愛<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTbNLRyNk9ZfMzkeL